; gap: 6px;&quot;&gt;Native Kubernetes — no extra infra needed&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;feature-item pro&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(15, 110, 86); line-height: 1.5; display: flex; gap: 6px;&quot;&gt;Great for ML and data processing jobs&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;section-title&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px 6px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(194, 192, 182); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em;&quot;&gt;Cons&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;feature-item con&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(163, 45, 45); line-height: 1.5; display: flex; gap: 6px;&quot;&gt;YAML can get very verbose and complex&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;feature-item con&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(163, 45, 45); line-height: 1.5; display: flex; gap: 6px;&quot;&gt;No built-in event triggering (needs Argo Events)&lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr class=&quot;divider&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-right: none; border-bottom: none; border-left: none; border-image: initial; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgba(222, 220, 209, 0.15); font-size: medium;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;section-title&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px 6px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; color: rgb(194, 192, 182); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em;&quot;&gt;Cannot do&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;feature-item cannot&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(194, 192, 182); line-height: 1.5; display: flex; gap: 6px;&quot;&gt;Listen to external events on its own&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;feature-item cannot&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(194, 19