 uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; font-family: &amp;quot;Anthropic Sans&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; text-align: start;&quot;&gt;Cons&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;feature-item con&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(163, 45, 45); line-height: 1.5; display: flex; gap: 6px; font-family: &amp;quot;Anthropic Sans&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; text-align: start;&quot;&gt;Replaces Deployment object — migration required&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;feature-item con&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(163, 45, 45); line-height: 1.5; display: flex; gap: 6px; font-family: &amp;quot;Anthropic Sans&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; text-align: start;&quot;&gt;Smaller project; fewer community resources vs CD&lt;/div&gt;&lt;hr class=&quot;divider&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; border-right: none; border-bottom: none; border-left: none; border-image: initial; border-top-style: solid; border-top-color: rgba(222, 220, 209, 0.15); font-family: &amp;quot;Anthropic Sans&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; font-size: medium; text-align: start;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;section-title&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 12px 0px 6px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(194, 192, 182); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.04em; font-family: &amp;quot;Anthropic Sans&amp;quot;, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &amp;quot;Segoe UI&amp;quot;, sans-serif; text-align: start;&quot;&gt;Cannot do&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;feature-item cannot&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 3px 0px; font-size: 13px; color: rgb(194, 192, 182); line-height: 1.5; display: f